or: red;\">基本上沒有廚房</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n他也坦言，<span style=\"color: red;\">煤氣跟電力的競爭很大</span>，「一條煤氣喉來到你家，入到廚房，是否代表你煮食會全用到煤氣？實際上並不如此，如你煲飯會用電飯煲，我相信有99%的香港人也用電飯煲煲飯，你煲湯很多時用電子瓦罉、壓力煲等，你早餐吃的多士也是用多士爐製作，也是用電的；以往用水煲煲水，現在大家也普遍改用電水煲，70年代後也出現了微波爐，其後也有電磁爐的出現，<span style=\"color: red;\">因此電力取了我們很多的市場</span>，電力跟我們有很大競爭。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過領展都唔好得幾多 比人炒到超貴 而且高增長期已過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2ac5bb046cd62864282065954f0571f74b1896","tid":1248380,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e624d572173956cf0be89c98173c4a4776623d27","tid":1248380,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f2ac5bb046cd62864282065954f0571f74b1896","tid":1248380,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"有何高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8027a51a9e899fe1976be6a3ef02cd9a8b3629f6","tid":1248380,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"183ab820d90231f3b1e8ba240a63b4c567481f82","tid":1248380,"uid":19065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a41d25e442198a7906fe6a2dd1c25c20fc3fefdd","tid":1248380,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"煤氣已到極限，跟住到中電發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你自己睇下中電個股價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"中電盈警"},{"pid":"64568835e8b209e9dde2d8918990296f8836bdbc","tid":1248380,"uid":218716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:31:35.000Z","msg":"仲咩領展煤氣，買M